  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Two ordinances calculated to ad-\njust the controversy over street\nspeaking will be presented at the\nmeeting of the city council this aft\nernoon as a committee of the whole,\nwhen II will take up the matter Of\namending the present street speak.\ning ordinance.\n\n\nThe ordinances have been pre-\npared by Fred II. Moore, attorney\nfor the Industrial Workers of the\nWorld. and will be accepted as sat\nisfactory by the crusaders for free\nspeech.\n\n\nThe first ordinance permits\nstreet speaking at any hour of the\nday, on half an hours notice in ad-\nvance being given to the police\nIn the case of an indecent, profane\nor improper language, the police are\nTO have the right to suppress the\ncpeaking."
    }
  ]
